        <num>CHC 1257</num>
        <heading>1257.  Change of name</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1257.  Change of name
The full name of the adopted child may be changed in the final decree of intrafamily adoption and, if changed, the surname shall be the same as that of the adoptive parent.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
